reviews.review_text:
lenny hart:  a history-making fuckup This show has never been a big favorite of mine but the audience recordings -- including this one -- are more interesting than the board recordings.  What a lovely sound!

This taper seems to have located himself in a postion that is relatively quiet (in terms of auidence noise) relative to where Jim Cooper was recording.
